query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_rows,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN isServiceable = 1 OR isServiceable IS NULL THEN 1 END) as serviceable_rows,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN (isServiceable = 1 OR isServiceable IS NULL) AND rateUsdCents IS NOT NULL THEN 1 END) as configured_rows
FROM supplierRates 
WHERE supplierId = 14;
